**Example 6.1:** We wish to carry out a depth first search of graph *G* of Figure 6.19(a). Figure 6.19(b) shows the adjacency lists for this graph. If we initiate this search from vertex <sup>V</sup>q, then the vertices of *G* are visited in the following order: vq, vj, V3, V7, V4, V5,
