As in the case of binary tries, we can define compressed tries in which each branch node has at least two children. In this case, each branch node is augmented to have an additional field \\textit{skip} which indicates the number of levels of branching that have been eliminated (alternately, we can have a field \\textit{sample} which indicates the sampling level to use).

